Summary: it looked exactly like a barbell.
divs: Sighting Detailsmy daughter and i were out fishing on the willamate river near canby oregon,about 3 hours into fishing i noticed a object north of myself but it kept "disapearing". finaly as i stood facing south watching my fishing pole tip i saw it again apear.i got out my bushnell binoculars,i take everywhere,and observed what was two orbs with a line connecting them,just like a barbell.the object was at extreamly high altitude and did move in a zig zag pattern when it moved.then it was gone.thought it was a star at first till ii looked with the binoculars.nope no star! was the first time i have seen a object of this shape in person.i have had other sightings but they are all orbs.single orbs.i have even got pics of hundreds of them,but nothing like this one.no pics sorry.but the time and date are exact.3.45 pm south of my location on 99 e.
